history.content:
LSCS 

January 26, 2018 - Deadline for all students to drop classes without a fee. $10 fee charged for each class dropped after this date.

February 2, 2018 - Deadline for all students to add classes without a fee. $5 fee charged for each class added after this date.

February 2, 2018 - Deadline to become “officially registered” (enrolled, tuition and fees paid, no blocks). $150 Late Registration fee after this date. 

February 16, 2018 - Deadline to add/drop classes. 

EECS

  • Early drop deadline
    Friday, January 26, 11:59 p.m.
  • Drop/add deadline
    Friday, February 16, 11:59 p.m.
  • Non-degree tech courses to pass/no pass
    Friday, February 16, 11:59 p.m.
  • H/SS pass/no pass deadline
    Friday, March 23, 11:59 p.m.
